	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Meminero quidem tuae intercessionis; sed magna est copia eorum, qui parum aut nihil habent, qui et ipsi sanctae sunt vitae et doctrinae probatae.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich wöllte, wir hättind vil ständ, das wir allen möchtend zuͦ hilff kommen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fama spargit patres <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName> postulasse a pontifice, ut se subiiciat concilio et iurament[a] ipsi praestita relaxet, quo liberius agere possint, quamobrem excanduerit pulpifex suspenderitque in ira illa sua sancta concilium per 4 menses.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certum illud est mense octobri <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinos</placeName> ad adventum Mantuani cardinalis exonerasse aut displosisse honoris ergo tormenta illa aenea maiora, incidisse autem ignem in pulverem pyrium et occidisse 18 personas, multo plures graviter sauciasse.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pestis gravissime sevit per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2560" cert="high">Austriam</placeName> et ascendere aut serpere dicitur adverso <placeName type="auto_name">Danubio</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> scribitur comitia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduni</placeName> celebrata inter legatos regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliae</placeName> et ducis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2478" cert="high">Sabaudiae</placeName>; reposcit ab hoc rex plurima, imprimis comitatum <placeName type="auto_name">Nissensem</placeName>; articuli sunt 6.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Negarunt Sabaudici omnia; legati regii diserte dixerunt regem haec ut sua repetere nec repetere tantum, sed et ius suum velle omnibus commonstrare.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legatus regis <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p629">Coignetius</persName> scribit ad me ex aula ultima novembris ac significat <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName> vehementer minari Gallis, nisi eiiciant haereticos, Gallos acres non magni facere minas; crescere autem ecclesias per totam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> plus, quam credi possit; futura comitia regni medio decembri, tentandum in his de rebus regni, maxime de religione promovenda cum pace.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orandus est dominus, ut piis conatibus adsit, impios dissipet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicit se post natalitias ferias rediturum in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam nunc accipio <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l210" cert="high">Haydelberga</placeName> literas ab amicis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eiecerunt rotundum panem ex actione coenae sacra et hoc mense coeperunt frangere panem; spes est summa rerum optimarum; princeps est optimus.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum sedulo, et ipse faciet.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Optimum illum senem nostrum benigne sufferto; <foreign xml:lang="de">er ist fromm fromm; die angfochtne ist sin praest.</foreign></s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta illum et communica ei ex his praecipua.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es düchte mich guͦt, wenn der schuldtheiß inn aller dingen bericht, und was ir anschlag, und das er wöllte zuͦfriden sin; man wölle der sach mitt sinem radt und wüssen rächt thuͦn etc.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">19. decembris 1561.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non relegi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Grüssend mir min schwager herr schuldheiß.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ille, qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, civi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Vitudurano</placeName>, domino suo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555" cert="high">Wintherdur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
